                        <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Unified under a common grid</h2>
                        <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">New modules and features don&rsquo;t have to be built from scratch. A powerful underlying grid can handle any combination of data that a user might need.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="inner-block half float-left relative">
