            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block case-full-image idauto-phone"></section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block not-padded idauto-white">
                <div class="inner-block half absolute-left vertical-center left-padded mobile-container" data-sr>
                    <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Engineered with an eye for detail</h2>
                    <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">We built the front-end in EmberJS, working with the client to define API functionality. We built not just an app, but the first step in a broader platform to serve future customers. And, the resulting code makes the design shine to the fullest.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="inner-block half float-right idauto-black relative">
                    <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/idauto/code-bg.svg" />
                    <img class="case-block-image absolute" src="../images/idauto/code-mobile.png" data-sr="enter bottom, move 800px" />
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block idauto-red">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="inner-block half left-padded absolute-right vertical-center mobile-padded-below mobile-container-absoalute" data-sr>
                        <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Bringing it to life</h2>
                        <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">Beautiful animations and visual feedback — progress bars, transitions, and validated input fields — make users feel in control, without wondering whether something worked.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="inner-block half float-left relative">
                        <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/idauto/duo-mobile-bg.svg">
                        <img class="case-block-image absolute" src="../images/idauto/duo-mobile-left-alt.png" data-sr="enter bottom, move 200px">
                        <img class="case-block-image absolute" src="../images/idauto/duo-mobile-right-alt.png" data-sr="wait .25s, enter bottom, move 200px">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block-flex not-padded view-three-quarter">
                <div class="inner-block half float-left padded mobile-container-extra idauto-off-white flex-center">
                    <h2 class="case-block-text-blockquote medium-length">Working with their team has been nothing short of amazing.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="inner-block half padded mobile-container idauto-green flex-center">
                    <div class="container flex-col">
                        <img class="case-block-text-quote-icon align-left" src="../images/idauto/quote.svg" data-sr="enter top, move 75px">
                        <p class="case-block-text-quote medium-length">&ldquo;It is rare to work with another company with the same passion for excellence as we have here at Identity Automation. We certainly see that same passion in Brave UX. Our experience working with their team has been nothing short of amazing. We are now seeing the fruits of their labor in our products today, and I am extremely happy with their work!&rdquo;</p>
                        <p class="case-block-text-citation">Troy Moreland, <em>Founder &amp; CTO, Identity Automation</em></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

